data.description: This spacious 4 bed, 2 bath house spans across 1572 square feet and is priced  at an attractive $150,000. Currently, the property is occupied by tenants who have a lease until the end of June. However, they are open to vacating earlier if provided with the right incentives. With its generous square footage and ample bedrooms and bathrooms, it presents an excellent opportunity for rental income or a comfortable home. One notable feature of this house is its new roof, which was installed in the fall of 2023. Property is being sold as-is.
